-- Apple shares hit fresh life high
-- 
-- Thu Jun 17, 2010 10:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/17/us-usa-stocks-apple-idUSTRE65G34O20100617

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of iPad maker Apple Inc ( AAPL.O ) hit a new lifetime high on Thursday, a day after the retail and technology bellwether said it sold more than 600,000 iPhone 4s, a record for a single day of preorders. 

 Shares hit $272.90 before slipping to $270.96, up 1.4 percent for the day. (Editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)